      "description": "Amazon SageMaker Serverless Inference (preview) enables you to deploy machine learning models for inference without configuring or managing any of the underlying infrastructure. With Serverless Inference, you only pay for the compute capacity used to process inference requests, billed by the millisecond, and the amount of data processed. The compute charge depends on the memory configuration you choose.",
